  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Kardias saves children&apos;s lives.  Our mission is to ensure that every Mexican child born with a congenital heart defect receives the best medical treatment available. We raise funds to support the outstanding doctors at the Children&apos;s Heart Center who are dedicated to providing critical treatment to children with congenital heart defects.  The Center was established in 2019 at the American British Cowdray Hospital, (The ABC Hospital), Mexico&apos;s finest not-for-profit private hospital.</narrative>
  </description>
